(Make sure it's all covered all the way over)

00:00:38.720 --> 00:00:40.900
(Oh look at that, well done)

00:00:40.900 --> 00:00:42.260
Step Two

00:00:42.860 --> 00:00:45.040
Okay Evie's gonna help me with this bit

00:00:45.040 --> 00:00:47.400
