00:00:55.170 --> 00:00:56.610
Make a claw with your hand

00:00:56.610 --> 00:00:59.330
as if you're digging your finger nails into the onion

00:00:59.330 --> 00:01:00.560
Using this as a guide

00:01:00.570 --> 00:01:04.610
slide the sharp side of the knife carefully through the onion

00:01:04.610 --> 00:01:06.910
Right now we're going to get them all in the pan

00:01:07.940 --> 00:01:12.200
