00:01:16.850 --> 00:01:18.110
(Good girl)

00:01:19.280 --> 00:01:21.540
Step Three

00:01:21.840 --> 00:01:23.040
Rinse the beans

00:01:23.040 --> 00:01:25.840
Right Archie you're going to pop those in. Nice and slowly

00:01:25.840 --> 00:01:27.560
And then add them to the pan

00:01:27.570 --> 00:01:29.470
Pour tin tomatoes

00:01:29.470 --> 00:01:32.180
(Ahh Arch! Brilliant)

00:01:32.180 --> 00:01:36.100
Tomato puree and chilli powder

00:01:36.880 --> 00:01:39.400
Here we go, sprinkle that in

00:01:39.400 --> 00:01:41.920
Brilliant, give it a good old stir

00:01:41.920 --> 00:01:44.660
Bring to the boil and simmer for twenty minutes

00:01:45.340 --> 00:01:47.060
Step Four

00:01:47.260 --> 00:01:49.100
(You take a big spoon then)

